<bibRefCitation author="Bezerra" box="[650,868,582,607]" pageId="10" pageNumber="11" refString="Bezerra, A. M. R., Carmignotto, A. P. &amp; Rodrigues, F. H. G. (2009) Small non-volant mammals of na ecotone region between the Cerrado hotspot and the Amazonian rainforest, with comments on their taxonomy and distribution. Zoological Studies, 48, 861 - 874." type="journal article" year="2009">
